item.title: US-26 East at NE-92
item.description: US-26 East at NE-92 in Broadwater. Turn right for NE-92 West; straight for US-26/NE-92 East.

item.title: US-26 East Approaching NE-92
item.description: US-26 East approaching NE-92 in Broadwater. Turn left for NE-92 west; continue straight for US-26 East/NE-92 East. NE-92 East joins US-26 eastbound to Lewellen.

item.title: US-26 East - Distance Marker
item.description: Distance marker on US-26 east. Distance to Broadwater, Oshkosh, and North Platte (via I-80).

item.title: US-385 North/US-26 East at US-385/US-26 Split
item.description: US-385 North/US-26 East at US-385/US-26 split in Morrill County.

item.title: US-26 East/US-385 North Approaching US-26/US-385 Split
item.description: US-26 East/US-385 North approaching US-26/US-385 split. Turn left for US-385 North to Alliance; left for US-26 East to Oshkosh.

item.title: US-26/NE-92 East at NE-92/US-385
item.description: US-26/NE-92 East at NE-92 East/US-385 in Bridgeport. Turn right for US-385 South/NE-92 East; turn left for US-26 East/US-385 North. US-385 North joins US-26 East through Bridgeport.

item.title: US-26/NE-92 East Approaching US-385
item.description: US-26/NE-92 East approaching US-385 in Bridgeport.

item.title: US-26 East at NE-92
item.description: US-26 East at NE-92 in Morrill County. Turn right for NE-92 West; left for US-26/NE-92 East.

item.title: US-26 East Approaching NE-92
item.description: US-26 East approaching NE-92. Use NE-92 West for Gering; US-26/NE-92 East for Bridgeport.

item.title: US-26 East Approaching NE-92
item.description: US-26 East Approaching NE-92 in Morrill County. NE-92 East joins US-26 east to Bridgeport. Chimney Rock is in the background of the photo.

item.title: US-26 East - Distance Marker
item.description: Distance marker on US-26 east. Distance to Bayard and Bridgeport.

item.title: US-26 East at NE-62A Link to US-385
item.description: US-26 East at NE-62A Link to US-385 in Morrill County.

item.title: US-26 East Approaching NE-62A Link
item.description: US-26 East approaching NE-62A Link. Use NE-62A Link East to Alliance (via US-385 north). Merge right to continue east on US-26 for Bayard and Bridgeport.

item.title: US-26 East Approaching NE-62A Link/To US-385
item.description: US-26 East Approaching NE-62A Link/To US-385. Turn right to continue east on US-26.

item.title: US-26 East - Morrill County
item.description: Entering Morrill County on US-26 east.
